    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. I have absolutely babied this car since the day I got it\u2014it\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage, hand-washed every weekend, and the interior still has that fresh, new-car smell! It\u2019s in truly pristine shape, looking and driving like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019m sad to let it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner so happy. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
