      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in exemplary mechanical condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear 333 hp power band. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a Variable M Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed, including a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. The chassis remains remarkably stiff, retaining original suspension geometry with no bushing deflection. This is a turn-key, analog performance icon with a pristine underside and matching numbers throughout.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
