    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a rare find for the discerning collector or enthusiast, presented in a state that can only be described as showroom-fresh. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like finish that has been protected by a high-end ceramic coating; there are absolutely no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Every panel alignment is factory-perfect. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of pristine materials. The premium leather seating remains supple and taut with no creasing on the bolsters, the carpets are spotless, and the interior still retains its original factory scent. All technological features and controls operate with precision, feeling as crisp as the day they were manufactured. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians. This car has been strictly garage-kept, never driven in inclement weather, and comes with a complete set of service records, all original keys, and the window sticker. It is, in every sense, a time-capsule vehicle for someone who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
